Items.mt: You are really kind-hearted and considerate. I will not go there, so that my emotions will not interfere with the work of the ninth mission, which is not good.

Items.r: 教主真是宅心仁厚、替人着想。老身就不前往了，以免因我的情绪干扰第九使办事，那可不好。
